### Admin Routes

### Get All Stores
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/stores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Store (Coordinates will be automatically geocoded if lat/lng are omitted)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/stores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "code": "HCM011",
  "name": "Store 1",
  "address": "123 Nguyen Hue, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "hotline": "0123456789"
}

### Create Store (without coordinates)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/stores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "code": "HN01",
  "name": "Hanoi Store",
  "address": "456 Hoang Quoc Viet",
  "hotline": "0987654321",
  "isActive": true
}


### Update Store 01
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/stores/f6088716-ca5e-4ed0-bef4-3dfe3abb51b8
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Store 1",
  "address": "123 Main St",
  "lat": 10.7757,
  "lng": 106.7009,
  "code": "HCM01",
  "hotline": "0123456789",
  "isActive": false
}

### Update Store 02
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/stores/f6088716-ca5e-4ed0-bef4-3dfe3abb51b8
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Store Ho Chi Minh",
  "address": "123 Nguyen Hue, District 1, HCM",
  "lat": 11.77343,
  "lng": 108.70323,
  "code": "HCM02",
  "hotline": "0909123456",
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Store
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/stores/75b95f24-ddc4-4c68-b1a7-753781c6ce7f
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Get Users List (Admin)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/users?page=1&limit=2&staff=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
### Update User
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/users/5c5133f2-796b-4e2b-9860-5c5aa1b9f4ea
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
{
  "isActive": true,
  "role": "MANAGER",
  "store_id": "58660bb9-cfd8-41f3-9cc6-989485b26d10"
}

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/users/5c5133f2-796b-4e2b-9860-5c5aa1b9f4ea
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get All Products (Admin)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Product (with image upload)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sku"

BURGER-IMG-01
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Burger With Real Image
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="basePrice"

19.99
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

{ "id": "2ae911b9-d2a1-4b1f-b053-92cec0e00463" }
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="burger.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./burger.jpg
--boundary--

### Create Product (JSON)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
{  
  "sku": "BURGER002",
  "name": "Classic Burger",
  "description": "Delicious beef burger with fresh vegetables",
  "type": "SIMPLE",
  "basePrice": 15.99,
  "costPrice": 8.50,
  "taxRate": 0.08,
  "thumbnail": "https://example.com/burger.jpg",
  "images": [
    "https://example.com/burger1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/burger2.jpg"
  ],
  "category": {
    "id": "2ae911b9-d2a1-4b1f-b053-92cec0e00463"
  },
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "preparationTime": 15
}

### Update Product (with image upload)
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products/66950321-f406-4a86-a5cf-2db8bf4fa776
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Updated Burger Name
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="new-burger.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./new-burger.jpg
--boundary--

### Update Product (JSON)
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products/prod-123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Classic Burger",
  "basePrice": 17.99,
  "isActive": false
}

### Delete Product
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products/66950321-f406-4a86-a5cf-2db8bf4fa776
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get All Categories (Admin)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/categories?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Category
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
{
  "name": "Foods",
  "slug": "",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Category
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/categories/cat-123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Foods",
  "slug": "",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Category
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/categories/cat-123
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get All Shipper Routes (Admin Dashboard)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/shipper-routes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Shipper Routes by Shipper ID (filter by specific shipper)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/shipper-routes?shipperId=SHIPPER_STAFF_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Force Refresh All Shipper Routes (Admin Dashboard - triggers solver)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/shipper-routes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
